description: Aardvark Ventures Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was involved in the acquisition, exploration, development, and mining of resource properties in North America. The company was formerly known as Roca Mines Inc. and changed its name to Aardvark Ventures Inc. in June 2021. Aardvark Ventures Inc. was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
